<measure quantity="9" unit="months">
<num value="9">九</num>月</measure>
<num value="43">丙午</num>
<pc>，</pc>徙烏古敵烈部於烏納水<pc>，</pc>以扼北邊之沖<pc>。</pc>冬<measure quantity="10" unit="months">
<num value="10">十</num>月</measure>
